_sText:
A luxurious Newport Beach mansion is being attacked by an anti-capitalist terror unit intent on bombing it to the ground.
They have specified two vulnerable targets - the walkway on the cliffside or the upstairs bathroom at the rear of the house. 

This map is perfect for around 12 players, but supports up to 56 for a full scale house war. It is fast paced, with several different routes encouraging tactical play.
